{"tid":332461,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 Pro Club 招人［兩閘 or 中堅]","createTime":"2017-07-23T04:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T14:19:37.000Z","uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c937b7a380e2026bd15972dba95816742a265211","tid":332461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"踢完HKVPL 後出局，因隊友踢法唔配合，所以想開一隊新隊招人一齊踢，睇下有無想離隊既好手一齊玩下，唔介意part time。<br />\n<br />\n基本上組軍已完成，但想繼續招左右閘 / 中堅，以適應其他戰術 (e.g 343)<br />\n<br />\n球隊一星期內已由D10升上D1 , 並且全部盃拎哂未降過班，所以對隊友技術要求都高，故謝絕新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n踢法：控傳原地反搶，技術流踢法，前鋒中場要hold 到波，如果打開鳩衝就不了。<br />\n<br />\n如有意試腳，請留低telegram，thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9984b35c946db18f0a247baa3511bf57e481f423","tid":332461,"uid":126502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Dossod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDossod&d=tADVYbgTlMUz%2BSzImxFTBr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0a00f7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dossod</a><br />\nCb"},{"pid":"d3559aaaa07915d1c1513a17ede94138bc7293b9","tid":332461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/Dossod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDossod&d=tADVYbgTlMUz%2BSzImxFTBr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0a00f7ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Dossod</a><br />\nCb</blockquote><br />\n已add telegram <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b885c9bbd22732deb536c3cc5547f0cb6c61ed0","tid":332461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"678a093eaf41d5b81cc1b261a3b9b79ee36dc550","tid":332461,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T11:02:58.000Z","msg